  "narrative": "# Turn 24\n\n*7 commanders issued orders this turn.*\n\n## Strategic Decisions\n\n### CURATOR (artifact collector)\n\nDispatched 4 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W25, W25, W19, W30.\n\n### NOMAD (merchant)\n\nDispatched 3 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W17, W9, W11.\n\n### PROPHET (apostle)\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 1 fleets; unloaded at 2 destinations; commissioned 5 new ships.\n\n### REAVER (pirate)\n\nDispatched 4 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W13, W8, W28, W18.\n\nEconomic activity: commissioned 7 new ships.\n\n### SOLARIS (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W4, W22.\n\n### TERRAN (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W14, W25.\n\nEconomic activity: invested in 1 units of industry.\n\n### TRADER (merchant)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W9, W22.\n\nEconomic activity: unloaded at 1 destinations.\n\n## Consequences\n\n### Territorial Shifts\n\n- **NOMAD** seized control of W17 (previously TRADER).\n\n### Fleet Movements\n\n- **CURATOR** moved: F7\u2192W25, F8\u2192W25\n\n- **NOMAD** moved: F15\u2192W17, F16\u2192W11\n\n- **REAVER** repositioned 4 fleets across the sector.\n\n- **SOLARIS** moved: F2\u2192W4, F1\u2192W22\n\n- **TERRAN** moved: F13\u2192W14, F14\u2192W25\n\n- **TRADER** moved: F3\u2192W9, F4\u2192W22\n\n### Production\n\n- **PROPHET** launched 5 new ships.\n\n- **REAVER** launched 7 new ships.\n\n- **TERRAN** built 1 industry.\n\n### Diplomacy\n\n- **TERRAN** sent a message to **SOLARIS**: *\"Alliance Proposal from TERRAN\"*\n"
